{"type":"message","id":"29deb357","parentId":"94bec047","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:03:08.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，Bitable 创建成功了。现在我需要创建合适的字段来存储评论数据。让我先看看当前有哪些字段，然后添加需要的字段。\n\n需要创建的字段：\n- 评论内容 (Text)\n- 作者 (Text)\n- 推荐状态 (SingleSelect: 推荐/不推荐)\n- 游戏时长 (Text)\n- 评论日期 (DateTime)\n- 问题类型 (MultiSelect: 崩溃/卡顿/Bug/优化/其他)\n- 关键词匹配 (Text)\n- 评论链接 (URL)\n- 处理状态 (SingleSelect: 待处理/已记录/已反馈/已解决)\n\n让我先创建这些字段。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cf43b4aa9eff47b78f9fdf30","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"评论内容","field_type":1,"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3dd19faeef7b452bb72aa48e","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"作者","field_type":1,"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a252340d2f0c4cbf8754f31e","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"推荐状态","field_type":3,"property":{"options":[{"name":"👍 推荐","color":"green"},{"name":"👎 不推荐","color":"red"}]},"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ccbd7d3c5814445a936a7d2a","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"游戏时长","field_type":1,"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_12a43a61346b46a4adfe64c9","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"评论日期","field_type":5,"property":{"format":"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm"},"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e4906315994f419fbba60ca4","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"问题类型","field_type":4,"property":{"options":[{"name":"崩溃/闪退","color":"red"},{"name":"卡顿/掉帧","color":"orange"},{"name":"Bug/错误","color":"yellow"},{"name":"优化问题","color":"blue"},{"name":"其他","color":"gray"}]},"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2bacffe741d541a4b8718cb5","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"匹配关键词","field_type":1,"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6ac418778f654c968793f323","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"评论链接","field_type":15,"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8c56d12bd43e463ca944228e","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"处理状态","field_type":3,"property":{"options":[{"name":"待处理","color":"yellow"},{"name":"已记录","color":"blue"},{"name":"已反馈","color":"purple"},{"name":"已解决","color":"green"}]},"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773709351749}}
