{"type":"message","id":"2e7ce97f","parentId":"d15d18d5","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:03:19.198Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"有些字段创建失败了，可能是 property 格式不对。让我重新创建那些失败的字段，使用正确的格式。\n\n失败的字段：\n- 推荐状态 (SingleSelect)\n- 评论日期 (DateTime)\n- 问题类型 (MultiSelect)\n- 处理状态 (SingleSelect)\n\n让我用正确的格式重新创建。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_68333e8f84b842f3ad142b52","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"推荐状态","field_type":3,"property":{"options":[{"name":"推荐"},{"name":"不推荐"}]},"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_186a1ff909fc4f9baff929ff","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"评论日期","field_type":5,"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2a1facf117d24d1ebae2ea82","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"问题类型","field_type":4,"property":{"options":[{"name":"崩溃/闪退"},{"name":"卡顿/掉帧"},{"name":"Bug/错误"},{"name":"优化问题"},{"name":"其他"}]},"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fd09fdade4f74ddf888d7e2b","name":"feishu_bitable_create_field","arguments":{"app_token":"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b","field_name":"处理状态","field_type":3,"property":{"options":[{"name":"待处理"},{"name":"已记录"},{"name":"已反馈"},{"name":"已解决"}]},"table_id":"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773709391493}}
