{"type":"message","id":"d0a392a1","parentId":"10db3615","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:04:01.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我已经创建了集成飞书的爬取脚本。现在需要告诉用户如何使用，以及需要配置飞书 API Token。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 已创建飞书集成版爬取脚本：`~/steam_review_crawler_feishu.py`\n\n**📊 飞书表格已就绪：**\n- 链接：https://xcnb9qtctplo.feishu.cn/base/YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b\n- 包含 9 个字段：评论内容、作者、推荐状态、游戏时长、评论日期、问题类型、匹配关键词、评论链接、处理状态\n\n**🚀 使用方法：**\n\n```bash\n# 1. 安装依赖\npip install requests\n\n# 2. 配置飞书 API Token (首次需要)\nopenclaw configure --section feishu\n\n# 3. 运行脚本\npython ~/steam_review_crawler_feishu.py\n```\n\n**脚本功能：**\n- ✅ 爬取 Steam 简体中文评论\n- ✅ 自动识别游戏问题关键词（崩溃、卡顿、Bug、优化等）\n- ✅ 自动分类问题类型\n- ✅ 上传到飞书表格\n- ✅ 保存 JSON 备份文件\n\n**⚠️ 注意：** 首次使用需要配置飞书 API Token。如果不想配置，脚本也可以只保存 JSON 文件，不上传飞书。\n\n需要我帮你配置飞书 Token 或者直接运行脚本吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773709429832}}
{"type":"message","id":"9419310f","parentId":"d0a392a1","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:05:07.700Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54bec2e0f0acb3768be3224fd4e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户154215\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-17 09:05 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户154215 (ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_689483ec5a555fe3639e3af84e52d8c3\",\n  \"name\": \"用户154215\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b54bec2e0f0acb3768be3224fd4e]\n用户154215: 除了简体中文评论  繁体中文也需要  只要是游戏问题不管是优化或者进不去、网络等 只要是问题就需要"}],"timestamp":1773709507698}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c98ecc3","parentId":"9419310f","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:05:47.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要：\n1. 同时爬取简体中文和繁体中文评论\n2. 只要是游戏问题都需要，包括优化、进不去、网络等问题\n\n我需要更新脚本：\n1. 添加繁体中文语言支持 (tchinese)\n2. 扩展关键词列表，包含更多问题类型（网络、进不去、登录、服务器等）\n3. 更新问题类型分类\n\n让我更新脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！我来更新脚本，支持简体中文 + 繁体中文，并扩展问题关键词范围。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00b42939faa243fbb1c99f2f","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"~/steam_review_crawler_feishu.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSteam 评论爬取脚本 - 飞书集成版 (简繁中文)\n爬取指定游戏的简体/繁体中文评论，筛选所有游戏问题相关评论并写入飞书表格\n\"\"\"\n\nimport requests\nimport json\nimport time\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# ========== 配置区域 ==========\n# 游戏 ID (从 URL app/3679080 获取)\nAPP_ID = \"3679080\"\n\n# 飞书配置\nFEISHU_APP_TOKEN = \"YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b\"\nFEISHU_TABLE_ID = \"tblKU26iyNNK3Ci0\"\nFEISHU_API = \"https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bitable/v1/apps\"\n\n# 语言配置：简体中文 + 繁体中文\nLANGUAGES = [\n    (\"schinese\", \"简体中文\"),\n    (\"tchinese\", \"繁体中文\")\n]\n\n# 问题关键词分类 (更全面的覆盖)\nISSUE_KEYWORDS = {\n    # 崩溃/闪退类\n    \"崩溃/闪退\": [\n        \"崩溃\", \"闪退\", \"黑屏\", \"白屏\", \"死机\", \"卡死\", \"无响应\",\n        \"crash\", \"freeze\", \"黑屏\", \"跳出\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 卡顿/性能类\n    \"卡顿/掉帧\": [\n        \"卡顿\", \"掉帧\", \"延迟\", \"lag\", \"卡顿\", \"不流畅\",\n        \"帧数\", \"fps\", \"慢\", \"卡\", \"性能\"\n    ],\n    \n    # Bug/错误类\n    \"Bug/错误\": [\n        \"bug\", \"Bug\", \"错误\", \"失败\", \"缺陷\", \"漏洞\",\n        \"异常\", \"报错\", \"出错\", \"毛病\", \"问题\", \"故障\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 优化类\n    \"优化问题\": [\n        \"优化\", \"配置\", \"配置要求\", \"硬件\", \"显卡\", \"CPU\",\n        \"内存\", \"发热\", \"功耗\", \"效率\", \"低效\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 网络/连接类\n    \"网络/连接\": [\n        \"网络\", \"联机\", \"在线\", \"连接\", \"服务器\", \"掉线\",\n        \"断连\", \"disconnect\", \"ping\", \"延迟\", \"卡顿\",\n        \"无法连接\", \"连不上\", \"进不去\", \"登录\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 启动/进入类\n    \"启动/进入\": [\n        \"启动\", \"打开\", \"进入\", \"加载\", \"载入\", \"初始化\",\n        \"无法启动\", \"打不开\", \"进不去\", \"黑屏\", \"白屏\",\n        \"launcher\", \"启动器\", \"验证\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 存档/进度类\n    \"存档/进度\": [\n        \"存档\", \"保存\", \"进度\", \"丢失\", \"损坏\", \"覆盖\",\n        \"save\", \"cloud\", \"云存档\", \"同步\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 音频/画面类\n    \"音频/画面\": [\n        \"声音\", \"音频\", \"音乐\", \"音效\", \"无声\", \"杂音\",\n        \"画面\", \"贴图\", \"渲染\", \"花屏\", \"模糊\", \"分辨率\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 操作/控制类\n    \"操作/控制\": [\n        \"操作\", \"控制\", \"按键\", \"键盘\", \"鼠标\", \"手柄\",\n        \"输入\", \"响应\", \"失灵\", \"无法操作\"\n    ],\n    \n    # 其他负面评价\n    \"其他问题\": [\n        \"失望\", \"差\", \"不好\", \"烂\", \"垃圾\", \"坑\",\n        \"后悔\", \"浪费\", \"不值\", \"期待\", \"希望改进\",\n        \"建议\", \"修复\", \"什么时候\", \"多久\", \"一直\"\n    ]\n}\n\n# ========== 飞书 API 函数 ==========\n\ndef get_feishu_access_token():\n    \"\"\"获取飞书访问令牌\"\"\"\n    try:\n        with open(\"~/.openclaw/feishu_token.json\", \"r\") as f:\n            token_data = json.load(f)\n            return token_data.get(\"access_token\")\n    except:\n        pass\n    return None\n\ndef create_feishu_record(fields):\n    \"\"\"在飞书表格中创建记录\"\"\"\n    access_token = get_feishu_access_token()\n    if not access_token:\n        print(\"⚠️  未配置飞书 API Token，跳过写入飞书\")\n        print(\"   配置方法：运行 'openclaw configure --section feishu'\")\n        return False\n    \n    url = f\"{FEISHU_API}/{FEISHU_APP_TOKEN}/tables/{FEISHU_TABLE_ID}/records\"\n    \n    headers = {\n        \"Authorization\": f\"Bearer {access_token}\",\n        \"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"\n    }\n    \n    data = {\"fields\": fields}\n    \n    try:\n        response = requests.post(url, headers=headers, json=data, timeout=10)\n        if response.status_code == 200:\n            return True\n        else:\n            print(f\"飞书 API 错误：{response.status_code} - {response.text}\")\n            return False\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"飞书请求失败：{e}\")\n        return False\n\n# ========== Steam 评论爬取函数 ==========\n\ndef fetch_reviews(language=\"schinese\", start_offset=0, num_reviews=100):\n    \"\"\"获取 Steam 评论\"\"\"\n    API_URL = f\"https://store.steampowered.com/appreviews/{APP_ID}\"\n    \n    params = {\n        \"json\": 1,\n        \"language\": language,\n        \"filter\": \"recent\",\n        \"start_offset\": start_offset,\n        \"num_reviews\": num_reviews,\n        \"day_range\": \"9223372036854775807\",\n        \"purchase_type\": \"all\"\n    }\n    \n    headers = {\n        \"User-Agent\": \"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36\"\n    }\n    \n    try:\n        response = requests.get(API_URL, params=params, headers=headers, timeout=15)\n        response.raise_for_status()\n        return response.json()\n    except requests.exceptions.RequestException as e:\n        print(f\"请求失败：{e}\")\n        return None\n\ndef analyze_review(text):\n    \"\"\"分析评论，提取问题类型和匹配关键词\"\"\"\n    matched_keywords = []\n    issue_types = set()\n    \n    text_lower = text.lower()\n    \n    for issue_type, keywords in ISSUE_KEYWORDS.items():\n        for keyword in keywords:\n            if keyword.lower() in text_lower:\n                matched_keywords.append(keyword)\n                issue_types.add(issue_type)\n    \n    # 去重\n    matched_keywords = list(dict.fromkeys(matched_keywords))\n    \n    return matched_keywords, list(issue_types)\n\ndef parse_playtime(playtime_forever):\n    \"\"\"解析游戏时长\"\"\"\n    if not playtime_forever:\n        return \"未知\"\n    hours = playtime_forever // 60\n    minutes = playtime_forever % 60\n    if hours == 0:\n        return f\"{minutes} 分钟\"\n    elif hours < 10:\n        return f\"{hours}小时{minutes}分\"\n    else:\n        return f\"{hours}小时\"\n\ndef save_reviews(reviews, filename=\"steam_reviews.json\"):\n    \"\"\"保存评论到 JSON 文件\"\"\"\n    with open(filename, \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        json.dump(reviews, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    print(f\"已保存 {len(reviews)} 条评论到 {filename}\")\n\ndef crawl_and_upload(max_pages_per_language=50, upload_to_feishu=True):\n    \"\"\"\n    爬取评论并上传到飞书\n    \n    参数:\n        max_pages_per_language: 每种语言最大爬取页数 (每页 100 条)\n        upload_to_feishu: 是否上传到飞书\n    \"\"\"\n    all_reviews = []\n    issue_reviews = []\n    uploaded_count = 0\n    stats = {}\n    \n    print(f\"🎮 Steam 评论爬取工具 - 简繁中文\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    print(f\"🎯 游戏 ID: {APP_ID}\")\n    print(f\"🌐 语言：简体中文 + 繁体中文\")\n    print(f\"📄 每种语言最多爬取 {max_pages_per_language} 页 (每页 100 条)\")\n    print(f\"📊 飞书上传：{'开启' if upload_to_feishu else '关闭'}\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    \n    for lang_code, lang_name in LANGUAGES:\n        print(f\"\\n{'='*60}\")\n        print(f\"🌏 开始爬取 {lang_name} 评论...\")\n        print(f\"{'='*60}\")\n        \n        stats[lang_code] = {\"total\": 0, \"issues\": 0}\n        offset = 0\n        \n        for page in range(max_pages_per_language):\n            print(f\"\\n📥 {lang_name} - 第 {page + 1} 页...\")\n            \n            data = fetch_reviews(language=lang_code, start_offset=offset)\n            \n            if not data or data.get(\"success\") != 1:\n                print(f\"❌ 无法获取{lang_name}评论，可能已达到最后一页\")\n                break\n            \n            reviews = data.get(\"reviews\", [])\n            if not reviews:\n                print(f\"✅ {lang_name} 没有更多评论了\")\n                break\n            \n            print(f\"   获取到 {len(reviews)} 条 {lang_name} 评论\")\n            stats[lang_code][\"total\"] += len(reviews)\n            \n            for review in reviews:\n                all_reviews.append({\n                    \"review\": review,\n                    \"language\": lang_code\n                })\n                \n                # 分析评论\n                text = review.get(\"review\", \"\")\n                keywords, issue_types = analyze_review(text)\n                \n                # 如果匹配到关键词，保存并上传\n                if keywords:\n                    issue_reviews.append({\n                        \"review\": review,\n                        \"language\": lang_code,\n                        \"keywords\": keywords,\n                        \"issue_types\": issue_types\n                    })\n                    stats[lang_code][\"issues\"] += 1\n                    \n                    # 上传到飞书\n                    if upload_to_feishu:\n                        fields = {\n                            \"评论内容\": text[:5000],\n                            \"作者\": review.get(\"author\", {}).get(\"steamid\", \"匿名\"),\n                            \"推荐状态\": \"推荐\" if review.get(\"recommendationid\") else \"不推荐\",\n                            \"游戏时长\": parse_playtime(review.get(\"playtime_forever\")),\n                            \"评论日期\": review.get(\"timestamp_created\"),\n                            \"问题类型\": issue_types if issue_types else [\"其他问题\"],\n                            \"匹配关键词\": \", \".join(keywords[:15]),\n                            \"评论链接\": f\"https://steamcommunity.com/app/{APP_ID}/reviews/?language={lang_code}\",\n                            \"处理状态\": \"待处理\",\n                            \"语言\": lang_name\n                        }\n                        \n                        if create_feishu_record(fields):\n                            uploaded_count += 1\n                            if uploaded_count % 10 == 0:\n                                print(f\"   ✅ 已上传 {uploaded_count} 条到飞书\")\n                        time.sleep(0.15)\n            \n            # 检查是否有下一页\n            total = data.get(\"query_summary\", {}).get(\"total_reviews\", 0)\n            if offset + 100 >= total:\n                print(f\"✅ {lang_name} 已爬取全部评论\")\n                break\n            \n            offset += 100\n            time.sleep(0.3)\n    \n    # 保存 JSON 备份\n    save_reviews(all_reviews, f\"steam_reviews_{APP_ID}_all.json\")\n    \n    # 保存问题评论 (纯数据)\n    issue_data = [item[\"review\"] for item in issue_reviews]\n    save_reviews(issue_data, f\"steam_reviews_{APP_ID}_issues.json\")\n    \n    # 保存分析后的问题评论\n    with open(f\"steam_reviews_{APP_ID}_analyzed.json\", \"w\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n        json.dump(issue_reviews, f, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2)\n    \n    # 统计汇总\n    total_reviews = sum(s[\"total\"] for s in stats.values())\n    total_issues = sum(s[\"issues\"] for s in stats.values())\n    \n    print(\"\\n\" + \"=\" * 60)\n    print(\"🎉 爬取完成!\")\n    print(\"=\" * 60)\n    print(f\"📊 统计汇总:\")\n    for lang_code, lang_name in LANGUAGES:\n        print(f\"   {lang_name}: {stats[lang_code]['total']} 条总评论，{stats[lang_code]['issues']} 条问题评论\")\n    print(f\"\\n📈 总计:\")\n    print(f\"   总评论数：{total_reviews}\")\n    print(f\"   问题相关评论：{total_issues}\")\n    if upload_to_feishu:\n        print(f\"   📤 已上传到飞书：{uploaded_count} 条\")\n        print(f\"   🔗 飞书表格：https://xcnb9qtctplo.feishu.cn/base/{FEISHU_APP_TOKEN}\")\n    print(f\"\\n📁 文件已保存:\")\n    print(f\"   - steam_reviews_{APP_ID}_all.json (全部评论)\")\n    print(f\"   - steam_reviews_{APP_ID}_issues.json (问题评论)\")\n    print(f\"   - steam_reviews_{APP_ID}_analyzed.json (分析后，含关键词分类)\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    # 检查是否安装了 requests\n    try:\n        import requests\n    except ImportError:\n        print(\"❌ 错误：需要先安装 requests 库\")\n        print(\"   运行：pip install requests\")\n        exit(1)\n    \n    # 询问是否上传到飞书\n    choice = input(\"\\n是否上传到飞书表格？(y/n, 默认 y): \").strip().lower()\n    upload = choice != \"n\"\n    \n    # 询问爬取页数\n    pages = input(\"每种语言爬取多少页？(每页 100 条，默认 50): \").strip()\n    max_pages = int(pages) if pages.isdigit() else 50\n    \n    crawl_and_upload(max_pages_per_language=max_pages, upload_to_feishu=upload)\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773709507700}}
