{"type":"message","id":"448a1857","parentId":"4cc1485b","timestamp":"2026-03-17T01:08:11.523Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"脚本已更新，现在使用 openclaw 网关的 feishu 命令来写入数据。让我帮用户直接运行这个脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ 脚本已更新！现在可以直接使用 openclaw 网关的飞书权限写入数据。\n\n**🚀 现在帮你运行脚本爬取数据吗？**\n\n脚本会：\n1. 爬取简体中文评论（最多 50 页 = 5000 条）\n2. 爬取繁体中文评论（最多 50 页 = 5000 条）\n3. 自动识别所有游戏问题（10 大类）\n4. 直接写入飞书表格\n5. 保存 JSON 备份\n\n**📊 飞书表格链接：** https://xcnb9qtctplo.feishu.cn/base/YwLebIyl1aC2KfsLBOacWivOn1b\n\n需要我现在运行吗？还是你想先调整爬取页数？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773709676951}}
