{"type":"message","id":"99c78402","parentId":"82db3e66","timestamp":"2026-03-17T09:38:44.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"飞书 drive 的 create_folder 可能需要 folder_token 参数来指定在哪个文件夹下创建。让我尝试使用 feishu_wiki 工具来创建知识库空间或节点，或者尝试在根目录下创建文件夹。\n\n根据 feishu_drive 的文档，create_folder 需要 name 参数，folder_token 是可选的（省略时为根目录）。但返回 400 错误，可能是权限问题或者 API 不支持。\n\n让我尝试使用 feishu_wiki 来创建知识库空间，这可能是更合适的方式来组织文档结构。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2171da66de374f408362d9b7","name":"feishu_wiki","arguments":{"action":"spaces"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773740319904}}
